---
title: Game Day Beef Chilli with Kidney Beans, Cheddar and Sour Cream
description: We're giving chili night an upgrade so that you can spend more time watching the game! Tonight’s chili is full of Mexican seasoned beef, fragrant veggies and hearty beans. A dollop of sour cream and a sprinkle of cheese finishes each bowl with a fresh and creamy touch.
